<p>You can use clsss <code>.table-clean</code> to remove default padding and borders.</p>
<p>If you need simple css driven table without grid, you can omit grid columns classes and use simple <code>div</code> as col.</p>
<div class="code-example">
    <div data-clone>
        <div class="table-css table-clean">
            <div class="row table-thead">
